      <scopecontent id="aspace_776ec89481c1a02360382127f61c56d1">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>These papers consist of records of the secretary of the Archaeological Institute of America, Connecticut Society. They include correspondence, financial papers of various types, minutes of business meetings, and miscellaneous papers concerning lecture series and membership.</p>
         <p>The papers were transferred to Manuscripts and Archives from Sterling Memorial Library in 1970.</p>
      </scopecontent>
